- Whenever text is placed within [brackets] -> a forth wall break is implied.

-Typically, the text within brackets will indicates what the game understands as input for that prompt.

-If you are stuck on a task and want to exit before it is completed, you must restart the game.

-There are random events that happen occasionally when traveling.

-Platinum Disks [PD] are the currency native to the realm.

-If a list of items is present, it will usually be presented in a table. The leftmost column indicates the ID number.
-the ID number is what you will enter to obtain the item.









